OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOvercast
OL,6,Fwith widespread low cloud soon
OL,7,Fdeveloping into the evening. Outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain will spread northwards across
OL,9,Fthe region during the night, some of
OL,10,Fwhich are likely to be heavy. Perhaps
OL,11,Fbecoming drier by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FCloudy start with some rain
OL,14,Faround, but brighter spells soon
OL,15,Fdeveloping through the morning.
OL,16,FIsolated showers then develop into the
OL,17,Fafternoon, perhaps heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
