OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FTurning cooler through this period,
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells and showers
OL,8,Fexpected, some of which may be heavy
OL,9,Fwith a risk of thunder. Winds
OL,10,Fgenerally light.
